<br>
My old guild used to have a level 56 minimum level requirement for ToV; just wasn't worth the hassle of healing people under 56.<br>
<br>
ToV is a place I would strongly recomend pet hold. Yes, if you are smart and paying constant attention you could get along without it, but just using /back off was a serious hassle and risk.<br>
<br>
With the new resist changes and pet heals, a high level mage should be able to keep their pet alive for awhile. If you have improved reclaim you could just suck up pets between fights and not lose any mana.  <p>Sage Cydmab Promethean <BR>
Arch Mage of Morell Thule <BR>
