<br>
I don't have the logs but I was able to only have to have 2 Epic Fights the entire fight Against Telk in ToV.  In fact my epic pet got the killshot. :d<br>
<br>
With the new resist changes on pets, and the non aggro issues, pets are much more welcomed at raids.  And IMO they can deal some dmg, next raid I plan on logging its dmg to see how well it does in ToV. <p><p><div align=left><table width="270" border="1" bgcolor="000000" cellpadding="5"><tr><td><DIV style="FILTER: glow(color=FFFF00); WIDTH: 100%; POSITION: relative" align=center><font face="Georgia, Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5" color="#000000"><I><a style="font-weight:bold; color:#FFFF00; text-decoration: none"href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=43987 >Dolekin Soothesayer</a></DIV></FONT></B></I><DIV style="FILTER:  Blur(Add = 1,Direction=225, Strength=20); WIDTH: 100%; POSITION: relative" align=center><font size="1" color="CCCCCC">Gnomish Conjurer of the 58th Season</font></DIV></tr></td></table></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left>

